.pl 66
                TABLE 7-2  AS ERROR CODES AND ERROR MESSAGES

 0.  Internal assembler error
 1.  Maximum location counter nesting exceeded (15)
 2.  Maximum if-endif nesting exceeded (15)
 3.  Open square bracket expected
 4.  Close square bracket expected
 5.  Open bracket expected
 6.  Close bracket expected
 7.  Comma expected
 8.  String delimiter expected
 9.  Length qualifier expected
10.  MMU register expected
11.  Processor register expected
12.  General-Purpose register (R0..R7) expected
13.  End of line or comment expected
14.  Unexpected character in input file
15.  Unexpected symbol
16.  Invalid instruction
17.  Missing operand
18.  Illegal operand
19.  Illegal operator
20.  Complex expressions not allowed for floating point
21.  Attribute of operand must be IMMEDIATE
22.  Configuration register expected
23.  Attribute of operand must be FLOAT or LONG
24.  Attribute of operand must be EXTERNAL PROCEDURE
25.  Floating point operand not allowed here
26.  Operand must be defined before use
27.  Attributes of operands do not match
28.  External operands must have the same ordinal number
29.  Division by zero
30.  Operand out of range
31.  Duplicate option specified
32.  Illegal addressing mode
33.  Illegal attribute of exported symbol
34.  Undefined symbol
35.  Symbol already declared
36.  EXPORT must precede symbol definition
37.  Illegal directive in this context
38.  Label required
39.  No label may appear on this directive
40.  Duplicate use of directive
41.  Illegal to decrement location counter in PC or SB segment
42.  Symbol type must be Immediate or Long
43.  Illegal relocation mode
44.  Nested procedure not allowed
45.  Illegal use of VAR
46.  Illegal use of BEGIN
47.  Illegal use of RETURN
48.  Unexpected ENDSEG or ENDPROC
49.  Return block size exceeds parameter block size
50.  Unbalanced if-endif

